<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{locale}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h1 style="color: #007bff;">OTP Verification</h1>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your verification code is:</p>
    <div style="background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h2 style="color: #007bff; margin: 0; font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 5px;">{{otpCode}}</h2>
    </div>
    <p>This code will expire in {{expiresIn}} minutes.</p>
    <p style="color: #dc3545; font-size: 12px;">⚠️ For security reasons, never share this code with anyone.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">Best regards,<br>LMS Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

